<p class="abstract">Unofficial capital of the country or not, it may take you a while to appreciate the magnetic charm of Milan. Right in the middle of Northern Italy, many think this city feels more European than Italian: churches, alleys and ancient ruins seems to be outnumbered by banks, offices and skyscrapers.</p>

